{"tid":1380453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 和理非自發不合作運動","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:59:24.000Z","uid":130568,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef452375d3a2e18a7ee8255fb3548f05f67cd9df","tid":1380453,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"730/85的罷工勢在必行，大家固然要參與<br />\n但罷工的行動難以持續，若罷工不能撼動政權，我地可以做ｄ乜？<br />\n<br />\n以下係其他我暫時聽到／諗到既可持續不合作運動<br />\n<strong>1. 零消費及全民凍省</strong><br />\n「凍」是凍結個人家庭消費，「省」是癱瘓公共場所，除了生理需要外，其他物品一律不消費。每天起床穿黑衣散步去車站、大型商場嘆冷氣，喝自己帶既水，去廁所，最緊要係不消費。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 不購買任何中資企業產品和服務</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 拎晒所有由中資提供既免費資源</strong><br />\n例如：大量拎中資旗下既免費報紙去回收、去書局打書釘<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 為自己居住的地方建立消費指南</strong><br />\n只光顧反送中立場的店舖 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 鍵盤戰士主動去深藍區域散播訊息</strong><br />\n不一定要筆戰，只需要不斷海量輸入反送中新聞同言論<br />\n<br />\n<strong>6. 所有有不反對通知書既遊行/集合都一定要去</strong><br />\n有反對通知書既就去行街，不求硬，如水流動<br />\n<br />\n大家可以提出自己覺得可行的方法，並按照自己既原則同能力去盡做，確切咁執行<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可，Now or Never<br />\n勇武和理非，放開彼此心中矛盾，理想一起去追<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同舟人 誓相隨 無畏更無懼</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"53affd69c14aff120259fbaaefd8b7fde2324f65","tid":1380453,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n<br />\n大家一齊支持下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bcf4fe2704bc32b3aae1207c8e325404df01ffd0","tid":1380453,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"b760854ba0f6b1519396614cba4d88240499f47e","tid":1380453,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"3f46cd33f3f6bd7299f296cad42a16d9cc57166f","tid":1380453,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"413ae949b98dc64f08428aa0312bdcdbcde08572","tid":1380453,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:14:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3437cd2d06d15c9c425415a4aae40cf1759a4781","tid":1380453,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"c8176252bb37c95d7a50fda335ff97f0e7a1878f","tid":1380453,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4956bc9107af8523372ffb51ce5d97ac66ab9e","tid":1380453,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"和理非戰略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1387789/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1387789/</a>"},{"pid":"620eceb7fcfea7b5306cb1a009a92cf7ad2f6743","tid":1380453,"uid":5662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6189a6dc68c76890383c2ba24b5802f5804042fe","tid":1380453,"uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fbc51c52b232d44e7665da343332904d6647ae5d","tid":1380453,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"同我推上去<br />\n<br />\n輿論戰都要同藍絲死過<br />\n 【都市擂台】對於有市民發起的「不合作運動」，你支持嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/f83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fpoll%2Ff83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67bZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=4dc2be4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/f83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98</a>"},{"pid":"c85974b5affad2480e10b499a51290cb85cc6046","tid":1380453,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:04:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n做得幾多得幾多"},{"pid":"e9830caaee463bb3b8220bfdded5dd6109e8a806","tid":1380453,"uid":130568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:49:37.000Z","msg":"星期一我會記錄(影底)有邊D食肆商店有響應罷工<br />\n如果寫到明支持罷工會再特別Mark底 <br />\n建立一個消費網<br />\n等大家玩得開心，食得放心<br />\n但一人之力有限，希望個個都做，起碼做自己生活既區域"},{"pid":"944bca74b9bc7a08c3700506209a8d8698d21a45","tid":1380453,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:58:14.